    "# Use Multiple Linear Regression to model salary based on location, job title, skills, remote type, employment type, minimum experience, and education level.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Load data\n",
    "# Multiple Linear Regression Salary Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "This section uses Multiple Linear Regression to predict salary from job posting characteristics. We first build a baseline model, then use feature ablation to identify which feature groups matter most. Based on the ablation results, we build an improved Model 2 and compare the two models.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Model 1: Baseline Multiple Linear Regression\n",
    "\n",
    "Model 1 predicts salary using seven main feature groups: location, job title, skills, remote work type, employment type, minimum years of experience, and education level."
